@startuml Observer Pattern Sequence Diagram
actor User
participant UI
participant Game
participant Observer

User -> UI: Clicks button (eventType)
UI -> Game: sendEvent(eventType)
Game -> Game: applyEventEffects(eventType)
Game -> Game: Update state machine
Game -> Game: notifyObservers()
Game -> Observer: update(gameState)
Observer -> UI: update(gameState)
UI -> UI: Update DOM
@enduml